# ==============================================================================
# Experimental Tab & New Sky (v1.1.0)
# ==============================================================================
screen.EXPERIMENTAL=சோதனை
screen.EXPERIMENTAL.comment=சோதனை

option.SKY_MODE=புதிய வானம் (வளிமண்டல சிதறல்)
option.SKY_STYLE=வான பாணி
option.SKY_STYLE.comment=Artistic direction for the physical sky. Realistic = true angular sizes & neutral colours (astronomy look). Semi-realistic = readable sun/moon (x2.8), richer colour, soft glow. Fantasy = grand sun/moon (x5.5), big corona, vivid teal/crimson/indigo palette.
option.SKY_MODE.comment=EXPERIMENTAL — off in all profiles. Gradient (legacy, default) or Physical realtime scattering with true multiple scattering (Rayleigh+Mie+Ozone, 1st+2nd+3rd order). Enable manually in this tab.
value.SKY_MODE.0=சாய்வு (பழையது)
value.SKY_STYLE.0=யதார்த்தமான
value.SKY_STYLE.1=அரை-யதார்த்தமான
value.SKY_STYLE.2=கற்பனை
